{"tid":271900,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[震驚七十億人] 發現鬆弛熊背後意義","createTime":"2017-06-05T12:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T17:38:18.000Z","uid":69512,"like":426,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f69ec3eb12b0c426fc5532042fd306ffe43e69d3","tid":271900,"uid":69512,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"一直都覺得鬆弛熊只係隻屎色好懶嘅熊，直到我見到呢幅圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/200925_1213559cd75c75fdfb4f706d20898ede.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F200925_1213559cd75c75fdfb4f706d20898ede.jpg&h=32d274a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n突然就明白鬆弛熊背後嘅含意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實鬆弛熊，白熊，豬鼻雞嘅膚色分別代表住黑人，白人，同黃種人，原來呢三隻野係宣揚緊種族共融嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地以為我9up?當然冇咁簡單啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地細心睇下就會發現佢地三個嘅size都係映射緊三種人條撚嘅size <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑人&gt;白人&gt;黃人 完全符合返我話佢地代表三個種族嘅論點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲打以後行街見到鬆弛熊嘅時候唔好忘記作者係背後嘅用心良苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1b145a8c165e1702b5585d724040b97f4eb966","tid":271900,"uid":21423,"like":141,"dislike":3,"score":138,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4cbea5860217cf44f48049bf1921bedf9f81b24","tid":271900,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:53:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃種人特別多雞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0bcb325c93adcac5d4ddde3815f1f92645faa3","tid":271900,"uid":48362,"like":131,"dislike":1,"score":130,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T12:54:58.0