cking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實鬆弛熊，白熊，豬鼻雞嘅膚色分別代表住黑人，白人，同黃種人，原來呢三隻野係宣揚緊種族共融嘅意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地以為我9up?當然冇咁簡單啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地細心睇下就會發現佢地三個嘅size都係映射緊三種人條撚嘅size <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑人&gt;白人&gt;黃人 完全符合返我話佢地代表三個種族嘅論點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲打以後行街見到鬆弛熊嘅時候唔好忘記作者係背後嘅用心良苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑色個隻個頭既size=差唔多6隻黃色個隻個頭既size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黑人大6倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}